{"id":12282,"date":"2024-02-23T17:07:44","date_gmt":"2020-07-23T11:37:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=12282"},"modified":"2023-05-08T14:11:25","modified_gmt":"2023-05-08T08:41:25","slug":"small-bedroom-storage-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Get Creative With 10 Sneaky Storage Ideas For Your Small Bedroom!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>When it&#8217;s about small bedrooms, storage is the biggest concern! Take cues from these 10 creative storage ideas for your small bedroom!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to live large in your tiny bedroom? The secret to success lies in your storage solutions. Proper storage solutions will keep your bedroom organised and clutter-free. And there are several creative storage ideas to keep your bedroom clean and tidy! For instance,you can choose multi-functional furniture to make the most of your bedroom space. So today we bring you 10 creative storage ideas to help you organise your bedroom and live an organised life.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So let&#8217;s take a look!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Hydraulic Bed: Where Comfort Meets Functionality<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your comfortable bed can serve as the ultimate storage solution&nbsp; for your small bedroom. Consider adding a hydraulic bed with storage as we see in this image here or a standard bed with storage drawers on either side. A bed with storage compartments and drawers can fit in every big or little thing you don&#8217;t use on a daily basis such as winter wear, luggage, blankets. Yes you can hide away literally everything!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163625\/hydraulic-bed-for-storage-in-small-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Hydraulic bed is a creative storage idea for small bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-12285\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163625\/hydraulic-bed-for-storage-in-small-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163625\/hydraulic-bed-for-storage-in-small-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163625\/hydraulic-bed-for-storage-in-small-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163625\/hydraulic-bed-for-storage-in-small-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make The Most Of Your Wardrobe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make use of every corner in your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/wardrobe-design\/\">wardrobe<\/a>. Install smart and creative storage solutions like racks, baskets and dedicated sections for all your belongings be it clothes, accessories, footwear or everyday essentials. This will help keep your wardrobe organised and bedroom clean all year long.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164401\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Small bedroom storage ideas with wardrobe to keep your wardrobe organised\" class=\"wp-image-12292\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164401\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164401\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164401\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164401\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Creative storage ideas for your small bedroom!\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/12181259\/creative-storage-ideas-for-your-small-bedroom.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Study Unit With A Secret Dresser<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A dressing unit is as important as a study desk in any bedroom regardless of its size. And we at Design Cafe understand that! This compact study unit with a hidden dresser is perfect for a small bedroom. This design turns the most basic element, a desk, into a stylish multi-functional piece of furniture. A simple desk with a lift-up shutter with a mirror and storage behind is a creative way to use this desk as a dressing unit.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164458\/storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms-with-study-unit-with-secret-dresser.jpg\" alt=\"Storage solutions for small bedrooms with a study unit with a secret dresser\" class=\"wp-image-12293\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164458\/storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms-with-study-unit-with-secret-dresser.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164458\/storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms-with-study-unit-with-secret-dresser-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164458\/storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms-with-study-unit-with-secret-dresser-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164458\/storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms-with-study-unit-with-secret-dresser-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Clean Change Is Just Around The Corner<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make the most of neglected areas of your bedroom &#8211; the corners! This pretty bedroom is small in size, but it&#8217;s packed with style, character, elegant colours and a customised corner storage solution! This corner storage idea features niches and a floating shelf to keep your books, decorative pieces and all the tiny knick-knacks that otherwise lie around in your bedroom! Stylish and sleek isn\u2019t it?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164308\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-customised-corner-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Small bedroom storage ideas with a customised corner storage solution\" class=\"wp-image-12291\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164308\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-customised-corner-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164308\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-customised-corner-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164308\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-customised-corner-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164308\/small-bedroom-storage-ideas-with-customised-corner-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Pull-Out Dresser<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want to know of a clever way to use your bedroom space? Try a pull-out dresser unit! This pull-out dresser is an L-shaped pull-out unit that goes back into the wall when not in use. It is designed with open boxed storage sections underneath. A full-length mirror can be installed above the same to make this unit fully functional in all aspects.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164059\/small-bedroom-storage-design-with-pull-out-dresser.jpg\" alt=\"Small bedroom storage design with a pull-out dresser\" class=\"wp-image-12289\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164059\/small-bedroom-storage-design-with-pull-out-dresser.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164059\/small-bedroom-storage-design-with-pull-out-dresser-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164059\/small-bedroom-storage-design-with-pull-out-dresser-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23164059\/small-bedroom-storage-design-with-pull-out-dresser-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Consider A Bench With Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Consider adding a bench or a box alongside one side of your bed to store things when not in use. Throw in extra pillows, quilts, blankets and even clothes! To keep your bedroom clean and clutter-free at all times with this simple solution that also does not occupy much space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163414\/easy-storage-ideas-for-small-bedrooms-with-bench-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Easy storage ideas for small bedrooms with a bench with storage\" class=\"wp-image-12283\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163414\/easy-storage-ideas-for-small-bedrooms-with-bench-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163414\/easy-storage-ideas-for-small-bedrooms-with-bench-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163414\/easy-storage-ideas-for-small-bedrooms-with-bench-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163414\/easy-storage-ideas-for-small-bedrooms-with-bench-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bedside Table With Dual Functionality<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A nightstand is a must! You must have heard this a lot, right? How about a nightstand with double duties? This uber-cool nightstand performs double functions &#8211; a drawer to store and an open shelf to flaunt your bestsellers along with a top base to mount a table lamp. A bedside table like this can be customised with different finishes and colours to match your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interior design<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163739\/multi-functional-bedside-table-storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms.jpg\" alt=\"Storage solutions for small bedrooms with a bedside table with multi-functionality\" class=\"wp-image-12286\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163739\/multi-functional-bedside-table-storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163739\/multi-functional-bedside-table-storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163739\/multi-functional-bedside-table-storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163739\/multi-functional-bedside-table-storage-solutions-for-small-bedrooms-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Hero Called Skirting Drawers<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This clever storage idea is the latest one! These simple skirting drawers help utilise dead spaces underneath wardrobes. They come out in a single push and can serve as a home to store your bills, warranty cards, paper bags and everything else that otherwise clutter your study desk or wardrobe drawers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163938\/skirting-drawers-storage-ideas-for-small-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Skirting drawers are clever storage ideas for small bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-12288\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163938\/skirting-drawers-storage-ideas-for-small-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163938\/skirting-drawers-storage-ideas-for-small-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163938\/skirting-drawers-storage-ideas-for-small-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163938\/skirting-drawers-storage-ideas-for-small-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hide It Behind The Door, In Style<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Space is the currency in a small bedroom that comes at a premium. Hence every element and object must perform double duties! Your closet or bedroom door can be an excellent storage idea to keep your shoes, handbags or accessories. All you need to do is fix basic hooks and hangers just like shown in this image here. You can simply shut the door, and no one will know what&#8217;s behind it. Sneaky isn&#8217;t it?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163516\/excellent-storage-idea-for-small-bedroom-behind-door.jpg\" alt=\"Creative storage ideas for small bedroom, behind the door an excellent storage idea\" class=\"wp-image-12284\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163516\/excellent-storage-idea-for-small-bedroom-behind-door.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163516\/excellent-storage-idea-for-small-bedroom-behind-door-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163516\/excellent-storage-idea-for-small-bedroom-behind-door-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163516\/excellent-storage-idea-for-small-bedroom-behind-door-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Play With Shelves<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Create a frame around your bed with open shelves to maximise your storage space to organise and flaunt all of your books, photo frames, decorative pieces. If you are <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/kids-bedroom-design\/\">designing a kids bedroom<\/a> use this space to store and display toys as shown in the image. The great thing about this storage idea is that you can customise it based on the colour scheme and size of your bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163838\/open-shelves-maximize-storage-in-small-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Maximize storage in small bedroom for kids with open shelves\" class=\"wp-image-12287\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163838\/open-shelves-maximize-storage-in-small-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163838\/open-shelves-maximize-storage-in-small-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163838\/open-shelves-maximize-storage-in-small-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/23163838\/open-shelves-maximize-storage-in-small-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For small bedrooms, where space is a premium, these creative storage ideas can help you make the most of it. You can further make your small bedroom appear big and spacious by incorporating bright colours, mirrors and ample light to create an illusion. Also to throw in rugs, curtains and indoor plants to make your small bedroom look like it&#8217;s straight out of a magazine!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>We hope these ideas help you make the most of your space!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/small-bedroom-design-ideas\/\">10 Best Small Bedroom Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/5-ideas-to-make-more-space-in-small-bedroom\/\">5 Ideas to Make More Space in Small Bedroom<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/space-saving-design\/\">Space Saving Designs by Design Cafe<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\